overview: When is a reality show more than a reality show? That's the question our L.A. ladies ask in Episode #18 (Real Life). When Lindsey jumps at the chance to work with a movie producer the film of her life, everyone wants in on the action. This "Sex and the City" take-off expects the gals to take it off - all off. It turns out this docu-drama is really a triple-X movie with Monica, Tori and Annie as the stars.
title: Naked Hollywood 18: Real Life
